headline: Royal Caribbean (RCL): Valuation Insights After Earnings Highlight Demand Uncertainty and Guidance Miss
summary: Royal Caribbean Cruises (NYSE:RCL) shares dropped sharply after the company released its third-quarter results. Despite reporting a jump in profits, the revenue and forward guidance missed forecasts. This has raised questions about demand trends and near-term industry headwinds. headline: 3 Large-Cap Stocks on Our Watchlist
summary: Large-cap stocks are known for their staying power and ability to weather market storms better than smaller competitors. However, their sheer size makes it more challenging to maintain high growth rates as they’ve already captured significant portions of their markets.
